					{ place } –º–µ—Å—Ç–æ
				</span>
			}
		</td>
		<td class="px-6 py-4">
			<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
				<div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 to-teal-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white text-xl flex-shrink-0">
					ü•ã
				</div>
				<div>
					<a href="/judoka" class="text-gray-900 font-semibold hover:text-teal-600 transition-colors">
						{ athlete }
